{"tid":2141444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一年前嘅今日系列］同大家回顧下8月6號發生咩事","createTime":"2020-08-05T16:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T23:44:30.000Z","uid":326820,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e362ada403a9be9cee09a37c1825c393dfe3f909","tid":2141444,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:27:54.000Z","msg":"大家好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係我，又同大家回顧下一年前嘅今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月6號 浸大學生會主席 方仲賢因為「購買武器」俾便衣黑警拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfzag1S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwfzag1S.png&h=8768bf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你以為咩武器咁把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係支觀星筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑警仲要自以為是咁示範俾記者睇啲觀星筆有幾危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KzhGuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KzhGuF.png&h=cdd716a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係香港人齊上齊落 一呼百應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大批人到天水圍警署聲援 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFtBW3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFtBW3E.png&h=42e979e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止咁，8月7號更加發揮香港人嘅創意，用觀星筆去太空館抗議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsN7jh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsN7jh6.jpg&h=4bf7d6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721, 85, 831呢啲大日子固然要記得，但係呢啲細啲嘅事都好值得哋記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7acfa5428cf887daffd740780f0b77149207fa","tid":2141444,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d42224c5e9c70727b985ace51eda5e9c2c538be","tid":2141444,"uid":352564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"未敢忘記，一路走來不易，大家保重"},{"pid":"fc6a95056190b5b0dd449fa078112fa2698399d3","tid":2141444,"uid":110509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"其實應該要出返本年史"},{"pid":"7fe2fd73e437348089bde2bb26496eda46543deb","tid":2141444,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"深水埗嚟"},{"pid":"fa1f84ae9354f2e39620512f7cf75fdc13f78df3","tid":2141444,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔係淨係得啲大日子值得記住<br />\n呢啲日子都好值得記住"},{"pid":"9bdc7ae3b3a23aa77713fd96ae34b5da7d5c2b76","tid":2141444,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fe2fd73e437348089bde2bb26496eda46543deb","tid":2141444,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"深水埗嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"我派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 